room_title: Escape room "Save the White House" by Escapehouse Chicago in Chicago
review: Agent Puccini was great to work with! We really enjoyed saving the White House today.

room_title: Escape room "Save the White House" by Escapehouse Chicago in Chicago
review: This was our second escape room experience. I think we are hooked! I am happy to report that we saved the White House with 15 minutes to spare! The clues were not easy but not extremely hard, either. We all worked well as a group, and I think that is why we finished with time to spare. The staff was fantastic and played their roles well. We enjoyed Agent Mask's humor and wit! Next time our boys are in town, we are going to attempt to escape the Safe House!

room_title: Escape room "Save the White House" by Escapehouse Chicago in Chicago
review: Great fun and fantastic opportunity to build team skills. Our agent director made it a memorable experience. We can't wait to come back!

room_title: Escape room "Save the White House" by Escapehouse Chicago in Chicago
review: Hi we just visited a couple weeks ago and escaped the Oval Office it was amazing!!!!! The experience was to die for!!!! We didn't know our groups but had an aweome time!!!
